metadata.name: IRU
metadata.description:
IRU/Darkness

I went through a depressing moment last year and lost myself. It was a difficult time for me to do anything productive , but slowly I tried making cool stuff in 3d and IRU was born. 

No matter how low you go , theres always something or someone to give you all the hope to push forward.

Chose Happiness.


Res 2048 x 2048
